      <title>阿斯利康股价创 14 个月来最差一周表现 因卖出买盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/astrazeneca-shares-set-for-worst-week-in-14-months-on-sell-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前英国制药商阿斯利康与合作伙伴第一三共株式会社的实验性肺癌药物发布令人失望的消息，导致两名分析师下调其评级，阿斯利康股价有望创下 2023 年 7 月以来的最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/astrazeneca-shares-set-for-worst-week-in-14-months-on-sell-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 10:09:37 GMT</pubDate>
