      <title>联合国未能打破银行僵局，利比亚石油产量进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/libyan-oil-flows-slide-further-as-un-fails-to-break-bank-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于联合国主导的谈判未能打破利比亚央行控制权僵局，且僵局已蔓延至利比亚石油行业，利比亚原油出口持续下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/libyan-oil-flows-slide-further-as-un-fails-to-break-bank-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德暗示欧洲央行可能在 10 月降息，但 12 月更有可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，如果经济遭遇重大挫折，欧洲央行愿意在 10 月份考虑降息——尽管下一轮全面信息要到下次会议上才能公布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称东京地铁将于下周公布股票 IPO 计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/tokyo-metro-is-said-to-unveil-700-billion-yen-ipo-plan-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，东京地铁公司预计将于 9 月 20 日公布其首次公开募股计划的细节，该计划可能使该公司的估值达到约 7000 亿日元（50 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/tokyo-metro-is-said-to-unveil-700-billion-yen-ipo-plan-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:34:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因恒大欺诈行为对普华永道处以创纪录罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-fines-pwc-halts-business-for-six-months-over-evergrande</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国因普华永道会计师事务所对中国恒大集团的审计存在疏漏，暂停了该事务所的运营六个月，并对其处以创纪录的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-fines-pwc-halts-business-for-six-months-over-evergrande</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
